  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to LXDM</title>

    <para>
      The <application>LXDM</application> is a
      lightweight display manager for<application>LXDE</application>. It can also be used as an
      alternative to <application>GNOME's</application><application>GDM</application> or
      <application>KDE's</application><application>KDM</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

